%% Diagram: Review submission with transactional outbox
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API as Review API
    participant PG as PostgreSQL
    participant Outbox as Outbox table
    participant Relay as Outbox relay (CDC / poller)
    participant Mod as Moderation worker
    participant ES as Elasticsearch
    participant Cache as Redis

    User->>API: POST /reviews { rating, text }
    Note over API,PG: Single ACID transaction
    API->>PG: INSERT review (status=pending)
    API->>PG: UPDATE business aggregates
    API->>Outbox: INSERT ReviewCreated event
    PG-->>API: COMMIT
    API-->>User: 201 Created (read-your-writes: visible to author)

    Relay->>Outbox: poll / tail WAL
    Relay->>Mod: ReviewCreated (Kafka)
    Mod->>Mod: spam + toxicity scoring
    alt auto-approve
        Mod->>API: PATCH status=approved
        API->>PG: UPDATE review + aggregates
        API->>ES: index/update business doc
        API->>Cache: invalidate geohash entries
    else manual review
        Mod->>API: PATCH status=manual_review
    end
